anything more, Colonel.

546
00:51:50,367 --> 00:51:55,202
"For distinguished duty in the face
of overwhelming... " something...

547
00:51:55,247 --> 00:51:56,805
- Odds.
- "... odds,

548
00:51:56,847 --> 00:52:00,726
