- "... McWatt. "

550
00:52:07,847 --> 00:52:09,917
Come on, come on.

551
00:52:14,087 --> 00:52:17,079
All right, McWatt.
What are you waiting for, a kiss?

552
00:52:17,127 --> 00:52:21,006
- Get back in there.
