575
00:54:00,567 --> 00:54:05,357
- You're a very weird person.
- Thank you, sir.

576
00:54:10,527 --> 00:54:12,722
- You are giving me this?
- Yes.

577
00:54:12,767 --> 00:54:14,962
- Perché?
